gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 126, Hawks 117
gameRecap.excerpt: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the Thunder with 30 points, eight rebounds, and six assists as the Thunder defeated the Hawks, 126-117. Lu Dort (19 points, nine rebounds) and Chet Holmgren (16 points, 12 rebounds, three blocks) totaled 35 points as Jalen Williams added 21 points for the Thunder in the win. Dejounte Murray led Atlanta with 29 points and six assists as Trae Young added 22 points, 11 assists, and four rebounds. Oklahoma City improves to 4-3 with the win as Atlanta moves to 4-3 on the season.
